      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense, but can u go deeper into the actual binding? like, what's happening at the active site of the COX enzymes? i need to understand how the ibuprofen molecule actually interacts with the enzyme to stop the reaction.",
      "source": "evaluator",
